(383, '2010-05-14', 99, 1405, 'Avon is the world''s leading direct seller of beauty and related products, reaching women in over 120 countries through 5.8 million independent sales Representatives.\r\nAvon offers an extensive range of products including make-up, skincare, fragrance, jewellery, lingerie, personal care, accessories and gifts.\r\nResponsible for managing the districts resources and executing the strategic efforts ensuring that Avon products and services effectively reach the districts consumers through the direct selling channel. The individual is the link between the Division Sales Manager and the Representative and has the responsibility of communicating both upward and downward while continuously motivating the Group Sales Leader and Representative to service the customers within the market. ', '', '', '', '', 'Dear Sir/Madam\r\n \r\nI herewith would like to apply for above vacancy. \r\n \r\nAttach please find a copy of my CV for your perusal.\r\n \r\nHope my application will be considered favourably.\r\n \r\nYours faithfully.\r\n \r\nMoira Stander\r\n0813737589 \r\n \r\n  \r\n \r\n\r\n', 62.5, 0, 31.25, 1, 0, 0, 0),
