(390, '2010-05-18', 100, 120, 'No.your intergrity & reputation suffers as decieving leads to poor service & lack of interest', 'my proper communications skills helped me to subdue and attend to the customers needs in a satisfactory way.', 'Hardworking\r\nconfident\r\nanalytical\r\nhighly self motivated', 'Yes.my current position has me directly linked to high end customer satisfation and responsibility.', 'Time management,my poor judgement let to a pile of paperwork and important tasks not to be aquainted to. ', 'APPLICATION FOR MANAGER\r\n\r\nI hereby apply for the above position.\r\nAs requested, I am enclosing a completed application letter, my certification, my resume and five references. The opportunity presented in this listing is very interesting, and I believe that my strong technical experience and education will make me a very competitive candidate for this position.\r\nThe key strengths that I possess for success in this position include:\r\nI am actively employed with compressive technical knowledge\r\n\r\nPlease see my resume for additional information on my experience\r\nI can be reached via email, office line or mobile phone\r\nSincerely,\r\nADMINISTRATOR\r\nTHOMAS E HISKIA\r\n18/5/2010\r\nhiskiate@mweb.com.na ThomasH@na.bellequipment.com', 66.67, 0, 33.34, 0, 0, 0, 0),
