(394, '2010-05-21', 100, 357, 'No, you can never deceive someone, there wil always be a way to be caught out, if you deceive someone else you deceive yourself..', 'a customer was being difficult to a cashier about the returns policy, shouting and saying that at other shops they werent so strickt. i walked up to the customer and nicely explained that were a top of the class shop and that our returns policy is to the best of every customer, we talked about the situation and sorted it out.', 'Hardworking, leader, good with staff, stamina, and handle stress good.', 'Yes, to be responsible is to be a great person, and i want to be the best person i can possibly be.', 'I resigned at a previous work because of racism from a co worker, i should have handled it differently, should have asked the person to stop being racist.', '', 66.67, 0, 33.34, 0, 5, 0, 0),
(395, '2010-05-21', 100, 749, 'Deception is wrong no matter what. The only exception however is only when the situation is life threatining.', 'I have dealt with very difficult customers in the past. I learned that the best way deal with them is to kill them with kindness. never argue, never tell them that they are wrong and I even blame yourself if necessary, make lots of eye contact, nod in agreement, make like you are listening, understand and care.', 'Determination, enthusiasm, friendliness, hate giving up\r\n', 'Yes I am. I have been tried and tested to be a responsible person via various ways. One of them being the SRC President of more than 11000 students at Polytechnic of Namibia.', 'So far I can not recall making a good decision.', '', 66.67, 0, 33.34, 0, 5, 0, 0),
(396, '2010-05-23', 100, 1686, 'no', 'A customer at my previous job received a drink which he paid for at the bar and 25min later returned to the bar asking to have his money back saying the waiter brought his drink to him with an insect in it, to calm him down offered him a small complimentary drink ank not of the same value and an appology from the waiter and he was happy.', 'Friendly, fair and respectful.', 'Yes I see myself as a responsible person I share a flat and have to budget my time and money accordingly, I like to bring this responsibility to a company, thus ensuring a stable working enviroment.', 'I had a chance to work in the Schoemans firm, as a printer techinician, I didn''t accept it, this I feel was my biggest mistake, and I don''t want to let a second chance slip through my fingers!', '', 66.67, 0, 33.34, 0, 5, 0, 0),
