(1465, '2010-11-02', 200, 765, ' ', 'Good organizational skills\r\nstrong communication skills\r\ngood listening skills\r\nhardworking\r\npassionate about working with people', '', '', '', ' M. Uises\r\n	P.O. Box 31863\r\n	Poinierspark\r\n	Windhoek\r\n	02 November 2010\r\nRE: GENERAL MANAGER\r\n\r\nDear Sir/Madam\r\n\r\nI would like to apply for the General Manager position, with 4 years experience as an Executive Secretary for West End Security Technology and experiences in secretarial and administration work, I worked independently with no need of on site-supervision; I was responsible for the day to day operations of the company like hiring and supervising any paid office staff and handled unusual problem', 100, 0, 50, 1, 0, 0, 0),
(1466, '2010-11-02', 195, 765, '', '', '', '', '', 'M. Uises\r\n	P.O. Box 31863\r\n	Poinierspark\r\n	Windhoek\r\n	02 November 2010\r\nRE: PUBLISHING AGENT\r\n\r\nI would like to apply for the Publishing Agent position, with 4 years experience as an Executive Secretary for West End Security Technology and experiences in secretarial and administration work, I worked independently with no need of on site-supervision; I was responsible for the day to day operations of the company like hiring and supervising any paid office staff and handled unusual problems under difficult circumstances.\r\n\r\nI provided materials and assistance in handling of company files and confidential documents. I maintained up to date filed records, handled all correspondence directed to the company. I provided all necessary and important information to the payroll service. I was responsible for filing and marinating all company records. I provided personal assistance to the executive members, also provided personal and confidential secretarial and professional support, drafted and typed routine correspondence, I received all incoming faxes and managed and screened all customer complaints and queries directed to the executive management.\r\n\r\nAs a Personal Assistant, the experience taught me the importance of clear communication and customer service on the telephone, I gained valuable business skills which will be an asset to any organization, and in addition I have acquired good customer skills. In my role as Personal Assistant/Administrative Assistant to the Manger of Xeneon Electro, I am required to manage a range of general administrative and specialized tasks in a timely and accurate manner. This includes managing a diary, organizing meetings, distributing agendas and mails, organize travel arrangements, accommodation and car hire. Typing of memos and letters assigned to me. I have advanced Microsoft Office skills and have used these to help produce the companys annual report and prospectuses.\r\n\r\nI am confident, well organized and friendly, and believe that my experience and skills will be an asset to your Company. Thank you for taking the time to consider my application. I look forward to the opportunity of meeting with you and discussing my candidacy for the position.\r\n\r\nYours Sincerely\r\nM.T. Uises\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
